Package: gwastargets
Title: GWAS Meta-Analysis Pipeline Functions
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person("First", "Last", email = "email@example.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Functions for multi-cohort GWAS meta-analysis supporting binary
    and quantitative traits. Provides harmonization, QC cleaning, allele
    matching, LDSC intercept correction, IVW meta-analysis, loci extraction,
    and targets pipeline code generation.
URL: https://mglev1n.github.io/gwastargets/, https://github.com/mglev1n/gwastargets
BugReports: https://github.com/mglev1n/gwastargets/issues
